    "description": "<p ><span >Make a <strong>DC 10 Spell Check</strong>.</span></p><p ><span ><strong>Success:</strong> Slick grease covers the ground in 4 Spaces of your choosing.</span></p><p ><span ><strong>Failure:</strong> Only 3 Spaces.</span></p><p ><span >The Spaces must connect to each other and all be within range of the spell. These Spaces are now considered to be Difficult Terrain for the duration and are flammable. If Fire touches these Spaces it ignites and deals 1 Fire damage to any creature within the Space instantly and again to any creature who ends their turn in this Space.</span></p><p ><span >If a creature is standing in Grease when the spell initially appears, when they end their turn, or if they enter an area with Grease, they must succeed on an <strong>Agility</strong> <strong>Save</strong> or fall </span><strong>@UUID[Compendium.dc20rpg.rules.JournalEntry.HNPA8Fd7ynirYUBq.JournalEntryPage.0wgHQIXjhxgu9i0s]{Prone}</strong><span >.</span></p><p ><span >Â </span></p><p ><span ><span ><strong ><span >Mana Point Enhancements</span></strong></span></span></p><ul ><li ><span ><strong>More Grease</strong><strong >: (1 MP) </strong>Add on 4 more Spaces</span></li><li ><p><span ><strong>More Fire:</strong> <strong >(1 MP) </strong>Make the Fire damage it deals if on fire increase by 1.</span></p></li></ul>",
